data.description: 2021 FULLY RENOVATED Mid Century Modern Van Story Hills. ¾ Acre private lot. 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, 2,879 SQFT on main floor, 997 SQFT partially finished basement. Large southern porch. Marble foyer leads to large formals with site-finished oak floors. Gourmet kitchen with custom cabinets, premium quartz countertops, ceramic tile, stainless appliance package with wall oven. Kitchen opens to spacious family room, lots of windows with refinished shutters facing back yard courtyard perfect for entertaining. Huge laundry and mudroom with partial bath. New shared bathroom, spacious bedrooms, remodeled master bedroom, walk in closet & completely new master bath with dual vanity & custom tiled shower. Wired playhouse in private backyard, lot backs up to Van Story Hills Elementary School. *** MULTIPLE OFFERS -- SELLER  has requests clients highest and best offer by Wednesday 6pm.****
